# Crash Bot Source Code

Welcome to the Crash Bot source code!

`Crash Bot` is Discord Bot software built with [discord.js](https://discord.js.org).

## Crash Bot Modules

The different services that Crash Bot provides are spilt into modules. Since Crash Bot is Discord-first software,
modules are defined primarily based on the functionality they provide through Discord.

Modules are built by first extending the Base Module class, then by referencing them in the entrypoint file (`index.ts`).

```typescript
// MyFirstClass.ts
import {BaseModule, OnClientEvent} from "./BaseModule";
import {Message} from "discord.js";

class MyFirstClass extends BaseModule {
    @OnClientEvent('messageCreate')
    onNewMessage(msg: Message) {
        // Whenever the bot receives a new message, do stuff here...
    }
}
```



```typescript
// index.ts
import {MyFirstClass} from "./myFirstClass.ts"

// ...
moduleClass = [
    ...,
    MyFirstClass
]
// ...
```